L. (1755)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="658">nom. illeg.</emphasis>
Conserved type (Jeffrey in Jarvis in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="658">Taxon</emphasis>
41: 566. 1992): Czech Rep., in ruderatis ad urbem Brno, ca. 180m, 15 Jun 1925, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Podpěra">Podpera</normalizedToken>
in Fl. Exsicc. Reip. Boh.-Slov. No. 946.11 (K).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
